My role within the team was handling the camera and video infrastructure, making sure everything integrated seamlessly with the other networks. I also built and managed a custom live timing page so everyone knew where they were supposed to be in real time for the duration of the festival. Since this was my lighting and video exam, I fulfilled many tasks during the show, including:

- Video Switcher
- Gimbal Operator
- Gimbal Assistant
- Lighting Operator
